com.github.liblevenshtein.transducer

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.liblevenshtein.transducer.State
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Position>

    public class State
extends Object
implements Iterable<Position>, Serializable
    Levenshtein state that is used by all algorithms. The algorithm-specific components are injected via setters, so State doesn't need to be coupled to specific implementations.
    Since:
    2.1.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
